@startuml
' Diagram: F02 - Tai va kham pha danh sach POI (Sequence)
' Status: WIP
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD 6510344
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/MainPage.xaml.cs: LoadPoisFromApi(), OnSearchTextChanged(), OpenPoiDetailAsync(), RecordPoiViewAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/PoiController.cs: GetAll()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/HeartbeatController.cs: RecordView()
' Note: Sequence da bam theo code MainPage hien tai; chua mo rong them luong ngoai repo va khong tu suy dien event nao khac.
title F02 - Tai va kham pha danh sach POI

actor Guest
participant MainPage
participant AppConfig
participant "PoiController" as PoiController
participant "HeartbeatController" as HeartbeatController
participant DetailPage
database DB

Guest -> MainPage: mo man Explore
MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
MainPage -> PoiController: GET /api/poi
PoiController -> DB: query POI dang hoat dong\nNgayHetHanDuyTri > now
DB --> PoiController: danh sach POI
PoiController --> MainPage: List<PoiDto>
MainPage -> MainPage: LoadMap()\nRenderPoiCards()

Guest -> MainPage: nhap SearchEntry
MainPage -> MainPage: OnSearchTextChanged()\nGetVisiblePois()\nRenderPoiCards()

Guest -> MainPage: bam "Xem chi tiet"
MainPage -> MainPage: OpenPoiDetailAsync(poi)\nRecordViewedPoi(poi)
MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/view
HeartbeatController -> DB: dedup 5 phut + insert LichSuPhat(Nguon="VIEW")
DB --> HeartbeatController: saved
MainPage -> DetailPage: PushAsync(new DetailPage(poi))

opt refresh nen 30 giay
  MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
  MainPage -> PoiController: GET /api/poi
  PoiController -> DB: query lai POI
  DB --> PoiController: danh sach moi
  PoiController --> MainPage: List<PoiDto>
  MainPage -> MainPage: LoadMap()\nRenderPoiCards()
end
@enduml
